  "title": "Benchmarking Notebooks for Production with FastAPI in Python 3.12+",
  "summary": "This guide demonstrates how to benchmark Jupyter notebooks for production-ready applications using FastAPI, a modern web framework for building APIs in Python 3.12+.",
