      "language": "Python",
      "code": "```\nfrom jupyter_client import connect_to_kernel\n\n# Load notebook kernel and get cell magic function\nkernel = connect_to_kernel()\nnb_magic = kernel.get_magics(['notebook'])\n\n# Define a FastAPI app with a route that executes notebook cells\ndef fastapi_app():\n    from fastapi import FastAPI, HTTPException\n    app = FastAPI()\n\n    @app.get('/execute-cell/{cell_number}')\n    async def execute_cell(cell_number: int):\n        cell = kernel.execute_cells([str(cell_number)], cell_metadata={'stream': True})[0]\n        if cell['status'] != 'ok':\n            raise HTTPException(status_code=500, detail='Error executing notebook cell')\n        return {'output': cell['output']}\n\napp = fastapi_app()\n```"
